body:
Suppose `test.v` is:
```
module bar();
	$dff a();
endmodule

module foo();
	bar b();
	$dff \b.a ();
endmodule
```
Run: `yosys test.v -p flatten`.

This will crash with an assertion:
```
ERROR: Assert `count_id(cell->name) == 0' failed in kernel/rtlil.cc:1557.
```

I plan to fix this issue as a part of my `flatten` improvements.

